text: Latehar' Sudeshwar Sadan Sinjo is a village of Manika Block in Latehar district, of Jharkhand. It is located around 120 km from Ranchi, the state capital. Sudeshwar sadan is located at K D M School Rd, Sinjo (Manika). ==External links== * Latehar district website * Latehar travel guide and maps Category:Latehar district Category:Community development blocks in Jharkhand Category:Community development blocks in Latehar district
